---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services" description="Executive AI Workshops, Strategy & Transformation, Custom AI Solutions.">

  <PageHero
    label="What We Do"
    title='We help leadership teams <span class="text-ms-green-400">make AI work</span> for their business.'
    subtitle="Not in theory. In practice. From the first workshop to a running system."
  />

  <section class="bg-ms-dark-800 border-y border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 space-y-16">

      <a href="/services/workshops" class="group block bg-ms-dark-700 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-10 hover:border-ms-green-500/30 transition-all">
        <p class="text-ms-green-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">01</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-ms-green-400 transition">Executive AI Workshops</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
          Your leadership team walks in unsure about AI. They walk out with a shared understanding and a prioritized action plan built on your actual business. Half-day or full-day. On-site or virtual. Prepared specifically for your company.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-ms-green-400 font-medium">Learn more →</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/strategy" class="group block bg-ms-dark-700 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-10 hover:border-ms-green-500/30 transition-all">
        <p class="text-ms-green-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">02</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-ms-green-400 transition">AI Strategy & Transformation</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
          From "we should do something with AI" to a funded strategy with clear milestones. Readiness assessment, use case identification, business case development, implementation support.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-ms-green-400 font-medium">Learn more →</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/halo-method" class="group block bg-ms-dark-700 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-10 hover:border-ms-green-500/30 transition-all">
        <p class="text-ms-green-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">03</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-ms-green-400 transition">The Halo Method</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
          Move from hierarchy to halo. A five-phase transformation that installs AI-driven coordination into your organization. We leave behind an operating system, not a recommendation.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-ms-green-400 font-medium">Learn more →</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/solutions" class="group block bg-ms-dark-700 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-10 hover:border-ms-green-500/30 transition-all">
        <p class="text-ms-green-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">04</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-ms-green-400 transition">Custom AI Solutions</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
          When the right tool doesn't exist, we build it. Internal AI assistants, decision support systems, process automation, designed for your workflows, integrated with your systems.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-ms-green-400 font-medium">Learn more →</p>
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA
    headline='Not sure where to start?'
    sub="Most clients begin with a discovery call. 30 minutes, no commitment. We'll help you figure out the right entry point."
  />

</Layout>
